message: "If you use this benchmark, governance bundle, or reproducer scripts, please cite both the manuscript and this Zenodo release."
type: dataset
title: "FAVES V4: Supporting Information — Benchmark, Governance, and Reproducer Scripts"
authors:
  - family-names: Harrison
